init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: A power only those capable of drawing upon the ancient Mana Tree seem to have.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And with it, they might just save themselves from extinction.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: In this new world, the mana tree has been reborn and all life is connected to it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Each person has a unique ability, and they will need to use that power to save the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The story will take a group of teenagers who have been together since birth, and follow them through their years in high school.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As they get older, the will learn more about their powers and how to use them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They will learn that there are people out there who want to take over the world and they will have to stop them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The people who have been chosen by the mana tree will all have different powers.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The people will be able to use the mana tree power to fight off the bad forces.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The people will have to fight against time because there are others who want to take over the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: There are people out there who want to do harm and they will use their powers against the good powers.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The characters will get stronger with age.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When they have gotten older they will be able to protect their world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: In the story, there is a man who will try to take over the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He wants to do pain and destruction.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The power that he has is very strong, so the characters will have to fight him off.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The group of friends will need to learn about their powers and how to control them so they can defeat the bad man.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The characters will have to put their powers together so they can defeat the man who wants to do harm.
